    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    AcousticGrandPianoStrategy
    Strategy for setting the instrument to Acoustic Grand Piano.
    ElectricBassGuitarStrategy
    Strategy for setting the instrument to Electric Bass (finger).
    HigherPitchStrategy
    Strategy for raising the pitch of a note by 2 semitones
    InstrumentStrategy
    Strategy interface for applying a specific instrument to a MIDI track.
    LegatoMidiEventFactory
    create note events with longer durations and minimal gaps between the NoteOff and the next NoteOn event.
    LegatoMidiEventFactoryAbstract
    An implementation of MidiEventFactoryAbstract that produces a LegatoMidiEventFactory.
    LowerPitchStrategy
    Strategy for lowering the pitch of a note by 2 semitones.
    Main
     
    MidiCsvParser
    MidiCsvParser reads a CSV file with MIDI note data and turns it into a list of MidiEventData objects.
    MidiEventData
    Represents a single MIDI event with all the necessary data tick, note, velocity, channel, instrument, and whether it's a note-on or note-off event.
    MidiEventFactory
    Interface for creating MIDI note events.
    MidiEventFactoryAbstract
    Interface for creating factory instances that generate MIDI events.
    PitchStrategy
    Strategy interface for modifying the pitch of a MIDI note.
    StaccatoMidiEventFactory
    A factory for creating staccato-style MIDI note events.
    StaccatoMidiEventFactoryAbstract
    A factory generator for staccato-style MIDI events.
    StandardMidiEventFactory
    A factory for creating standard MIDI note events with normal durations.
    StandardMidiEventFactoryAbstract
    A concrete factory generator for standard MIDI events.
    TrumpetStrategy
    Strategy for setting the instrument to Trumpet.
